{"tid":1469081,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"吸取前車之鑑，團結不割席，不指責","createTime":"2019-08-14T00:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:42:32.000Z","uid":43785,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c4c6066637bbd878d35933d6bd069a8d190b98","tid":1469081,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:26:30.000Z","msg":"嗰啲屌前線嘅人，阻到記者醫護又點喎？警察開槍打記者醫護添，佢哋有冇屌自己前線手？即係你班人仲衰過警察，核爆都不割蓆邊個講？做人可以做錯事，但係唔可以做壞事。阻到記者醫護可能係錯事，但係你哋捉鬼屌前線一定係壞事。<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼係口號<br />\n放核彈都唔割都係口號<br />\n不撒不散都不過係口號<br />\n係囉，原來大家真係講下笑，叫下就算。咁何必咁辛苦出去叫呢？<br />\n<br />\n吸取前車之鑑，團結不割席，<span style=\"color: red;\">不指責</span>！"},{"pid":"64ef2e3ab679eebf1be35a70e9d5ce96a4e6f32a","tid":1469081,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:27:17.000Z","msg":"吸取前車之鑑，團結不割席，不指責"},{"pid":"a9ffcfbdf9aa211d414dda4ce9c6d6455d4ee435","tid":1469081,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfaxdxi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnfaxdxi.png&h=6ab68e6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"610bfeaf4d941ef4b3bec72dc9ee9e756e589ed6","tid":1469081,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:31:18.000Z","msg":"鳩sir 講野我地要知， 就係港共政府派人嚟（可以係任何角色）令你示威者群眾闘群眾。"},{"pid":"3f04101b8ca3012f37bd2a1bd04841cfba522df4","tid":1469081,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833f160a7bcb528ad0ea229d11c56601aa8ea13e","tid":1469081,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,